(25, 'it_31', 0, '服务器', '', '<p>asc是指定列按升序排列，desc则是指定列按降序排列</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--wamp安装后访问/phpmyadmin报错，原有是phpmyadmin和MySQL的账号密码对不上</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--解决-&gt;phpmyadmin修改密码：apps/phpmyadmin4.1.14/config.inc.php修改[&#39;password&#39;]=&#39;新密码&#39;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--解决-&gt;wamp桌面右下角的图标找到MySQL-&gt;MySQL console，输入新密码，重启wamp就好了<span style="color: rgb(165, 42, 42);">(家里测试不用这步也能正常访问sql界面，且不用输账户密码)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(165, 42, 42);">--公司用</span>phpmyadmin4.1.14能打开sql界面，但adodb某语法版本太低报错，修改后页面还是不显示数据库的内容但也不报错；加里用WampServer Version 2.1(phpmyadmin3.3.9)都能正常运作</p>\r\n', '2016-11-02 06:34:26', '2017-12-30 02:52:05', 12),
