(211, 0, '19-08-03', NULL, '<p>- 昨晚跟刘先生语音11:30到早上6:20</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- tomcat视频教程：<a href="https://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTIxMTIxMDY4.html?spm=a2h0j.11185381.listitem_page1.5~A&amp;&amp;f=3773779">https://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTIxMTIxMDY4.html?spm=a2h0j.11185381.listitem_page1.5~A&amp;&amp;f=3773779</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 虚拟主机，批处理文件.bat，集成web服务器</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- web服务器软件：IIS,Apache,,Tomcat</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 拓扑图</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 二进制形式，Binary</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- JDK</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- jar - war文件</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- DNS服务器</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- 部署描述符文件：web.xml</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- telnet</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- Host头字段</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- TCP，超时</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Editor VS IDE (webstrom / vsCode)</p>\r\n', '2019-08-03 06:30:07', '2019-08-04 02:01:25', 1),
