(335, 0, '', 0, '<p>用状态管理工具的好处：<br />\r\n1）如果全局变量是对象，引用关系的变量改变了不会被检测并更新到视图<br />\r\n状态管理必须同过mutation来修改值，会被检测到并自动渲染视图<br />\r\n2）组件间参数和方法不需要层层传递，每个组件只要跟状态管理器交互就好了，更扁平化？</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div>computed: {</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">xxx: {</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">get () { return yyy;},</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">set (val) {} // 如设置this.xxx = val会不停循环执行；如设置yyy = val则不会更新到视图</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">}</div>\r\n\r\n<div>}</div>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nwindow.VM = new Vue(...)<br />\r\n可以在http.js中通过window.VM.$store来访问全局状态</p>\r\n', '2019-04-20 10:07:39', '2019-04-20 10:10:50', 4),
(336, 0, '', 0, '<p>el-tree</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class="hljs php" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.93em; padding: 1em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; line-height: 1.45; word-break: break-all; background: url(&quot;../img/blueprint.png&quot;) 0% 0% / 30px, 0% 0% / 30px rgb(246, 246, 246); border: none; border-radius: 4px; max-height: 35em; position: relative; margin-top: 0px !important;">\r\n<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; padding: 0px; color: inherit; background: none; border-radius: 0px; white-space: inherit; overflow-wrap: normal;">设置已选项：this.$refs.tree.setCheckedKeys([]);</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n&lt;el-tree :props=&quot;treeProps&quot; ...</pre>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\ntreeProps: {\r\n    children: &#39;children&#39;,\r\n    label: &#39;label&#39;\r\n}</pre>\r\n\r\n<p>// 可通过:props修改数据结构的字段</p>\r\n', '2019-04-28 06:19:09', '2019-05-06 09:25:36', 4),
