(195, '', 0, 'RESTful', NULL, '', '<p><span style="font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">REST（英文：</span><span style="font-weight: 700; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Representational State Transfer</span><span style="font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">，简称</span><span style="font-weight: 700; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">REST</span><span style="font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">）</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>这个词组的翻译是&quot;表现层状态转化&quot;。</li>\r\n	<li>表现层&quot;其实指的是&quot;资源&quot;（Resources）的&quot;表现层&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>把&quot;资源&quot;具体呈现出来的形式，叫做它的&quot;表现层&quot;（Representation）</li>\r\n	<li>如果一个架构符合REST原则，就称它为RESTful架构。</li>\r\n	<li>URI应该只代表&quot;资源&quot;的位置，它的具体表现形式，应该在HTTP请求的头信息中用Accept和Content-Type字段指定</li>\r\n	<li>HTTP协议里面，四个表示操作方式的动词：GET、POST、PUT、DELETE。它们分别对应四种基本操作：GET用来获取资源，POST用来新建资源（也可以用于更新资源），PUT用来更新资源，DELETE用来删除资源</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">视频教程：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.imooc.com/learn/811" target="_blank">http://www.imooc.com/learn/811</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-安装chrome插件：DHC REST client</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-状态码：200,204,400,401,403,404,500,503...</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-CURD</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-http默认端口80；https默认端口443</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height: 14px;">RESTful API 设计指南：<a href="http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2014/05/restful_api.html" target="_blank">http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2014/05/restful_api.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>理解：</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2011/09/restful.html" target="_blank">http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2011/09/restful.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://kb.cnblogs.com/page/512047/" target="_blank">http://kb.cnblogs.com/page/512047/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>三种web服务交互方案：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-RESTful</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-SOAP(Simple Object Access Protocal) - 简单对象访问协议</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-XML-RPC</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>工具：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- PostMan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- DHC</p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-07 07:35:26', '2019-03-15 17:33:48', 25),
(196, '', 0, 'gulp安装', NULL, '', '<p>参考网址：http://blog.wangdaodao.com/2015-04-21/hello-gulp.html<br />\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>dos根目录转到e盘：<br />\r\ne: 回车</p>\r\n\r\n<p>转到本盘下的目录：<br />\r\ncd AppServwww ode est</p>\r\n\r\n<p>最后执行里面的js文件：<br />\r\ntest2.js</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(上面两部可以用以下一句代替：AppServwww ode est est2.js回车)<br />\r\n(如测试根目录，输入node test2.js回车)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>gulp安装到全局：<br />\r\nnpm install -g gulp<br />\r\n再安装到根目录：<br />\r\nnpm install gulp --save-dev</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>gulp内的模块安装：<br />\r\nnpm install gulp-less gulp-minify-css gulp-uglify gulp-imagemin --save dev</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>各模块功能：<br />\r\n[gulp-less:less编译成css]<br />\r\n[gulp-minify-css:压缩css]<br />\r\n[gulp-uglify:压缩js]<br />\r\n[gulp-imagemin:压缩图片]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>gulp如不指明文件名默认被执行文件为gulpfile.js，<br />\r\n如不指明任务名默认被执行名为default的任务；</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>gulpfile.js内输入以下执行任务脚本:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>//加载相应模块<br />\r\nvar gulp = require(&#39;gulp&#39;),<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; less = require(&#39;gulp-less&#39;),<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; minifycss = require(&#39;gulp-minify-css&#39;),<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; uglify = require(&#39;gulp-uglify&#39;),<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; imagemin = require(&#39;gulp-imagemin&#39;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// less编译<br />\r\ngulp.task(&#39;less&#39;, function() {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; return gulp.src(&#39;less/media.less&#39;)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(less())<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(gulp.dest(&#39;less2&#39;))<br />\r\n});</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// css压缩<br />\r\ngulp.task(&#39;css&#39;, function() {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; return gulp.src(&#39;css/media.css&#39;)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(minifycss())<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(gulp.dest(&#39;css2&#39;))<br />\r\n});</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// js压缩<br />\r\ngulp.task(&#39;js&#39;, function() {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; return gulp.src(&#39;js/h_base.js&#39;)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(uglify())<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(gulp.dest(&#39;js2&#39;))<br />\r\n});</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// img压缩_单个<br />\r\ngulp.task(&#39;img&#39;, function() {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; return gulp.src(&#39;imgs/aaa.png&#39;)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(imagemin())<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(gulp.dest(&#39;imgs2&#39;))<br />\r\n});</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// img压缩_整文件夹<br />\r\ngulp.task(&#39;imgs&#39;, function() {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; return gulp.src(&#39;images/*.{png,jpg,gif}&#39;)<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(imagemin())<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(gulp.dest(&#39;images2&#39;))<br />\r\n});</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>gulp.task(&#39;default&#39;,[&#39;task1&#39;,&#39;task2&#39;],function(){...});</p>\r\n\r\n<p>任务执行顺序：task1 &gt; task2 &gt; default</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>cmd输入 gulp 执行default任务，以上即执行task1 &gt; task2 &gt; default</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>执行单个任务：<br />\r\ngulp less</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>自定义兼容IE的gulpfile.js文件：<br />\r\n------------<br />\r\nIE8及以下版本不支持less，为了测试此兼容，在先用js把style截取放到新less文件，<br />\r\n再执行gulp任务来编译成css，同时copy一个测试html并让其调用css文件；<br />\r\n---/000/web/_static/for_review/gulpfile备份的gulpfile.js已有实现上述功能的完备代码；</p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>关于环境变量：<br />\r\n------------<br />\r\nwin7--&gt;计算机右击-&gt;属性-&gt;左栏高级系统设置-&gt;高级/环境变量<br />\r\n--分为&ldquo;用户变量&rdquo; &amp; &quot;系统变量&quot;;<br />\r\n--在PATH后面添加对应的路径来添加环境变量；</p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-07 03:09:31', '2016-12-07 03:10:19', 70),
(197, '', 0, 'node安装', NULL, '', '<p>node.js说明：<br />\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n--测试环境：win7系统 / 本机DOS根目录：C:\\Users\\alex<br />\r\n--参考：jingyan.baidu.com/article/b0b63dbfca599a4a483070a5.html<br />\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n--安装<br />\r\nnodejs的官网：https://nodejs.org/en/download/ &nbsp;-&gt; 下载 Windows Installer ;<br />\r\n双击安装程序安装;<br />\r\n打开安装后的nodejs文件夹点击npm文件来安装此环境<br />\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n--使用<br />\r\n-&gt;开始-&gt;输入cmd(回车调出DOS窗口);<br />\r\n输入&ldquo;node&rdquo;回车即可进入node.js交互模式<br />\r\n输入&quot;.exit&quot;可以退出node<br />\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n--测试<br />\r\n进入node.js交互模式后输入console.log(&quot;Hello World!&quot;);<br />\r\n回车下一行就会显示Hello World!字样<br />\r\n----------------<br />\r\n根目录建test.js：<br />\r\nconsole.log(&quot;Hello World 2!&quot;);<br />\r\ndos输入node test.js<br />\r\n回车下一行就会显示Hello World 2!字样<br />\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n--less编译测试<br />\r\n安装less : Dos里直接输入 npm install -g less -&gt; 回车后提示一堆东西（带各种颜色的英文）<br />\r\n如此less安装到了C:\\Users\\alex\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm中;<br />\r\n把Bootstrap/less/media.less放C:\\Users\\alex中;<br />\r\nDos里输入lessc media.less &gt; ccc.css 回车；<br />\r\n这样就把less 编译成了css 在C:\\Users\\alex生成了一个ccc.css文件。<br />\r\n卸载less： npm uninstall -g less<br />\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n--css压缩测试 [参考：http://www.oschina.net/p/clean-css/]<br />\r\n安装clean-css : Dos里直接输入 npm install clean-css -g 回车；<br />\r\nDos里输入cleancss -o eee_min.css ccc.css 回车 -&gt; 生成的压缩文件把原文件的注释和空格全删掉了；<br />\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n--js压缩测试<br />\r\n安装uglifyjs : Dos里直接输入 npm install uglify-js -g 回车；<br />\r\n把一脚本文件h_base.js放C:\\Users\\alex中;<br />\r\nDos里输入uglifyjs h_base.js -o h_base-min.js 回车 -&gt; 生成的压缩文件把原文件的注释和空格全删掉了；<br />\r\nDos里输入uglifyjs h_base.js -o h_base-min2.js 回车 -&gt; 生成的压缩文件把原文件的注释和空格全删掉+都加密了；<br />\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n多个模块安装：<br />\r\n输入:npm gulp-a gulp-b gulpc 回车；</p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-07 03:10:16', '2016-12-07 03:10:13', 70),
(198, '', 0, '安装插件', NULL, '', '<p>安装插件：<br />\r\n--进入https://packagecontrol.io/installation<br />\r\n--复制对应的安装代码；<br />\r\n--把代码黏贴到编辑器的控制器里(view-&gt;Show Console)回车；<br />\r\n--安装好后重启编辑器；<br />\r\n--ctrl+shift+p打开命令模式找到&quot;package Control:Install package&quot;(可输入pc即可)点击进入到可安装的package列表；<br />\r\n--找到想安装的package点击即能安装；</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bootstrap snippet :<br />\r\n--ctrl+shift+p命令模式里可选择组件等类名即能自动把整个组件的html都写出来了！</p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-07 03:10:57', '2019-03-02 05:56:50', 30),
(199, '', 0, '矢量图标制作', NULL, '', '<p>自定义矢量图标制作过程：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--矢量图标的制作：AI软件用高宽均为512px文档来制作图标，完成后保存为SVG格式</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--打开网址https://icomoon.io/app,逐个上传用到的图标，都确认被选择上，点击右下方&ldquo;Generate Font&rdquo;生成，再点击&ldquo;download&rdquo;下载到电脑（也可以选择该站提供的图标来生成）；</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--解压后的fonts文件夹和style.css的必要的，通过添加对应类名(如.icon-star)和样式表内设置font-family(如:font-family:&#39;icomoon&#39;可以调用;)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>@font-face自定义字体详解：<br />\r\nhttp://www.w3cfuns.com/thread-5597432-1-1.html<br />\r\nhttp://www.jb51.net/css/106175.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p>@font-face制作Web Icon 三种方法：<br />\r\nhttp://www.xiaohai.cc/post/57.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p>自制矢量图标过程： &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nhttp://www.3lian.com/edu/2015/01-06/187209.html</p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-07 03:12:38', '2016-12-07 03:12:36', 70),
(200, '', 0, 'less基础', NULL, '', '<p>官网：<a href="http://www.bootcss.com/p/lesscss/" target="_blank">http://www.bootcss.com/p/lesscss/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>less函数：</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://less.bootcss.com/functions/" target="_blank">https://less.bootcss.com/functions/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://lesscss.cn/functions/" target="_blank">http://lesscss.cn/functions/</a></p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-07 03:46:37', '2019-01-04 14:58:07', 86),
(201, '', 0, 'gulp-模块-requirejsOptimize', NULL, '', '<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; width: 600px;">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><span style="line-height: 16px;"><strong><span style="color:#B22222;">gulp-requirejs-optimize</span></strong>：</span></td>\r\n			<td><span style="line-height: 16px;">--</span>把require的脚本文件包含其所有依赖一起合并压缩</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>--通过exclude把不需要一起合并的共用文件排除</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">安装</span>：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">$ npm install --save-dev gulp-requirejs-optimize</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">示例</span>：&nbsp;(合并压缩js)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">------------------------</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 224);">gulp.task(&#39;scripts&#39;, function () {</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 224);">&nbsp; &nbsp; return gulp.src([&#39;resource_pre/js/*.js&#39;,&#39;!resource_pre/js/require.js&#39;])</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 224);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(requirejsOptimize(function(file) {</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 224);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;return {</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 224);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;exclude: [</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 224);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;lib/jquery-1.10.2.js&quot;,</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 224);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&#39;layout/common.js&#39;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 224);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;]</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 224);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;};</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 224);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}))</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 224);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(gulp.dest(&#39;resource/js&#39;));</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 224);">});</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 34, 34);">相关网址</span>：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">https://www.npmjs.com/package/gulp-requirejs-optimize</span></p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-07 05:56:03', '2016-12-06 18:40:00', 27),
(202, '', 0, 'gulp基础', NULL, '', '<p>http://www.gulpjs.com.cn/docs/getting-started/</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style="color: rgb(178, 34, 34);"><span style="font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">gulp.src的base属性</span></span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">gulp.src(script</span><span class="hljs-regexp" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">/lib/</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">*.js) </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class="hljs-comment" style="color: green; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">//没有配置base参数，此时默认的base路径为script/lib</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> </span><span class="hljs-comment" style="color: green; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">//假设匹配到的文件为script/lib/jquery.js</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> .pipe(gulp.dest(</span><span class="hljs-string" style="color: rgb(163, 21, 21); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">&#39;build&#39;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">)) </span><span class="hljs-comment" style="color: green; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">//生成的文件路径为 build/jquery.js</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">gulp.src(script</span><span class="hljs-regexp" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">/lib/</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">*.js, {</span><span class="hljs-string" style="color: rgb(163, 21, 21); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">base:</span><span class="hljs-string" style="color: rgb(163, 21, 21); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">&#39;script&#39;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">}) </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class="hljs-comment" style="color: green; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">//配置了base参数，此时base路径为script</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> </span><span class="hljs-comment" style="color: green; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">//假设匹配到的文件为script/lib/jquery.js</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> .pipe(gulp.dest(</span><span class="hljs-string" style="color: rgb(163, 21, 21); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">&#39;build&#39;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">)) </span><span class="hljs-comment" style="color: green; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap;">//此时生成的文件路径为 build/lib/jquery.js </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--配置文件中baseUrl也是入口文件p_index的相对路径，测试不能用../p_index.js来跳到上一级</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--rconfig.js为不影响入口文件不设置baseUrl，可另外自定义一个path变量，但gulp执行时貌似不识别拼接地址中的此变量</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(178, 34, 34);"><strong>gulp.watch：</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>--指定某*.less一改变就执行task为less的任务，gulpfile.js写法如下：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">//监听</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">gulp.task(&quot;watch&quot;,function(){</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &nbsp; gulp.watch(Path.src.less+&#39;*.less&#39;,[&#39;less&#39;])&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">});</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>--创建当前目录的命令行快捷文件：watch.bat,内容如下：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">call gulp watch</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">pause</span>:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-07 06:25:58', '2016-12-06 18:47:21', 27),
(203, '', 0, 'gulp-模块-gulp-jade', NULL, '', '<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--npm install gulp-jade //安装</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--npm install gulp-plumber //jade报错</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--gulpfile.js写法：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">gulp.task(&#39;jade&#39;,function(){</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &nbsp; return gulp.src(Path.src.baseUrl+&#39;*.jade&#39;)</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe($.plumber())</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe($.jade({</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; pretty: true //转化的html不压缩</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &nbsp; }))</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &nbsp; .pipe(gulp.dest(Path.dest.baseUrl))</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">});</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--global.jade如下：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">body</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; block header</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; div.header 顶部</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; block content</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &nbsp; div#content 内容</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; block footer</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; div.footer 底部</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--index.jade可以这么写：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">extends global.jade</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">block content&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;div#content &lt;p&gt;111&lt;/p&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;div class=&quot;main&quot;&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;p&gt;222&lt;/p&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">上面得到：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&lt;body&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &lt;div class=&quot;header&quot;&gt;顶部&lt;/div&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &lt;div id=&quot;content&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;111&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;main&quot;&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &lt;p&gt;222&lt;/p&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &lt;/div&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&nbsp; &lt;div class=&quot;footer&quot;&gt;底部&lt;/div&gt;</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color: rgb(230, 230, 250);">&lt;/body&gt;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--jade直接写html时换行退格键会报错，换行不用退格键不报错</p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-07 06:41:02', '2016-12-06 18:42:43', 27),
(204, '', 0, '基础', NULL, '', '<p>速查表：<a href="http://jquery.cuishifeng.cn/regexp.html" target="_blank">http://jquery.cuishifeng.cn/regexp.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>视频教程：<a href="http://www.imooc.com/learn/706" target="_blank">http://www.imooc.com/learn/706</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>var patt=new RegExp(pattern,modifiers);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>简写：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>var patt=/pattern/modifiers;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>pattern：正则表达式</p>\r\n\r\n<p>modifiers：修饰符（<span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">放在正则表达式的最后，当参数使用</span>）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">i&nbsp;- 不区分大小写的匹配。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">g&nbsp;- 全文的搜索（而不是在找到第一个就停止查找,而是找到所有的匹配）。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">m</span>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">mutiple允许多行匹配</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>示例：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>var re = new RegExp(&#39;w+&#39;,&#39;g&#39;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>var re = /w+/g;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>//&nbsp;后向引用,也叫反向引用,就是将正则表达式的匹配结果临时存储起来,供以后调用</p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-07 09:54:52', '2019-01-16 07:08:21', 63),
(205, '', 0, '获取地理位置', NULL, '', '<p><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">原理：</span>navigator对象新增了属性geolocation</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">var x=document.getElementById(&quot;demo&quot;);</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">function getLocation(){</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">if (navigator.geolocation){</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;"><span style="color:#FF0000;">navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition</span>(success,error);</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">} else {</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">x.innerHTML=&quot;Geolocation is not supported by this browser.&quot;;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">function success(pos){</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">x.innerHTML=&quot;Latitude: &quot; + pos.coords.latitude +</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">&quot;&lt;br /&gt;Longitude: &quot; + pos.coords.longitude;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">function error(er){</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">&nbsp; &nbsp; console.log(&#39;失败&#39;)</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>---------------------------------------------------------</div>\r\n\r\n<div>getCurrentPosition() // 获得用户的位置</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">参数一：成功回调函数。返回的数据有：</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">coords.latitude<span style="white-space:pre"> </span>十进制数的纬度</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">coords.longitude 十进制数的经度</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">coords.accuracy<span style="white-space:pre"> </span>位置精度</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">coords.altitude<span style="white-space:pre"> </span>海拔，海平面以上以米计</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">coords.altitudeAccuracy<span style="white-space:pre"> </span>位置的海拔精度</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">coords.heading 方向，从正北开始以度计</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">coords.speed 速度，以米/每秒计</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">timestamp<span style="white-space:pre"> </span>响应的日期/时间</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">参数二：失败回调函数</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">参数三：一个选项对象，用于设定信息的类型。可以设置的选项有三个：</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">- enableHighAccuracy是一个布尔值，表示必须尽可能使用最准确的位置信息；</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">- timeout是以毫秒数表示的等待位置信息的最长时间；</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 80px;">- maximumAge表示上一次取得的坐标信息的有效时间，以毫秒表示，如果时间到则重新获 得最新坐标信息</div>\r\n\r\n<div>---------------------------------------------------------</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- watchPosition() - 返回用户的当前位置，并继续返回用户移动时的更新位置（就像汽车上的 GPS）。</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- clearWatch() - 停止 watchPosition() 方法</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>百度地图：</div>\r\n\r\n<div>秘钥：http://lbsyun.baidu.com/apiconsole/key</div>\r\n\r\n<div>（我用的是七度27的账号）</div>\r\n\r\n<div>html里引用&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;http://api.map.baidu.com/api?v=2.0&amp;ak=你的秘钥&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;就能调用它的api了</div>\r\n\r\n<div>API地址：http://lbsyun.baidu.com/index.php?title=jspopular</div>\r\n\r\n<div>实例地址：http://lbsyun.baidu.com/jsdemo.htm#a1_2</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>http://www.runoob.com/html/html5-geolocation.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p>http://www.cnblogs.com/tinyphp/p/3949015.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">利用百度地图和谷歌地图接口获取用户地址：</strong>http://www.jb51.net/html5/317651.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>api:http://developer.baidu.com/map/reference/index.php?title=Class:%E6%80%BB%E7%B1%BB/%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E7%B1%BB<br />\r\n全面：http://justcoding.iteye.com/blog/2210367</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\ngps不需要网络：http://bbs.csdn.net/topics/392055712?list=lz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>强制打开gps：http://blog.csdn.net/android_ls/article/details/8605931&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nhttp://blog.aizhet.com/PHP/14646.html<br />\r\n- Android大部分机型会存在获取地理位置超时 的情况<br />\r\n国行Android由于被阉割了谷歌的GMS服务，导致能正常调用 getCurrentPosition 函数但永远无法触发回调<br />\r\n在经过测试后，发现部分国内厂商的浏览器对 getCurrentPosition 进行了重新的封装，其中UC、QQ浏览器都已经重新封装了但对于国际大厂的浏览器由于没有考虑到我国特殊情况所以一律都超时<br />\r\n大部分智能手机都能很好的支持 getCurrentPosition<br />\r\n系统被阉割、不完善等不可抗力的原因这个能怪谁？而且有时候问题太特殊了</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>http://www.cnblogs.com/panhe-xue/p/5902108.html</p>\r\n\r\n<p>百度地图or高德地图：https://www.zhihu.com/question/23758141</p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-07 10:32:23', '2018-12-26 18:00:25', 53);
INSERT INTO `point` (`id`, `pid`, `sort`, `title`, `attr`, `description`, `extend`, `subFieldSet`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`, `lineId`) VALUES
(206, '', 0, '历史记录_history', NULL, '', '<div>问题：</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- 如何获取所有历史记录的state?</div>\r\n\r\n<div>- 如何做成无刷新跳转</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>h5之前的接口：</div>\r\n\r\n<div>history.back(); //后退一步，等同history.go(-1)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>history.forward(); // 前进一步，等同history.go(1)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>新接口：</div>\r\n\r\n<div>history.<span style="color:#FF0000;">pushState</span>(data,title,url);</div>\r\n\r\n<div>参数一是给state的值；</div>\r\n\r\n<div>参数二为页面的标题，但当前所有浏览器都忽略这个参数，传个空字符串就好；</div>\r\n\r\n<div>参数三是你想要去的链接；</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>history.<span style="color:#FF0000;">replaceState</span>(data,title,url);</div>\r\n\r\n<div>跟pushState方法的用法基本相同，</div>\r\n\r\n<div>不同的是它并没有往历史记录中增加记录，而是直接替换了当前的url，页面也是没跳转；</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="color:#FF0000;">popstate事件</span>：监听浏览器后退、前进的操作</div>\r\n\r\n<div>window.addEventListener(&quot;popstate&quot;,function(e){&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>console.log(e.state);</div>\r\n\r\n<div>},false);</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>属性：</div>\r\n\r\n<div>history.length // 历史堆栈条目</div>\r\n\r\n<div>history.scrollRestoration // 是否自动滚动到我们之前浏览的位置，默认auto，不自动设置成manual</div>\r\n\r\n<div>history.state // 返回一个堆栈顶部的状态，状态是pushState和replaceState加进去的</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">原理：history对象新增了属性pushState &amp;&nbsp;replaceState</span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">- history.go();</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">- history.pushState &amp; replaceState &amp; window.onpopstate</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">(https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/DOM/Manipulating_the_browser_history</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">http://www.cnblogs.com/flash3d/archive/2013/10/23/3384823.html)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">- localhost.hash</p>\r\n\r\n<p>pushState</p>\r\n\r\n<p>replaceState</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>去掉url的hash：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;-&nbsp;window.location.hash=&quot;&quot;; //这方法还是会留下一个#</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;-&nbsp;history.replaceState(null,&#39;&#39;,&#39;&#39;);</p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-18 13:11:00', '2018-12-26 18:01:38', 53),
(207, '', 0, '原生JS', NULL, '', '<p><code class="js keyword" style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; background: none !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; font-weight: 700 !important; min-height: auto !important; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; border-radius: 0px !important; color: rgb(255, 120, 0) !important;">var</code>&nbsp;<code class="js plain" style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; background: none !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; min-height: auto !important; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; border-radius: 0px !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;">str&nbsp;=&nbsp;</code><code class="js string" style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; background: none !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; min-height: auto !important; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; border-radius: 0px !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 255) !important;">&#39;11122233344s&#39;</code><code class="js plain" style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; background: none !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; min-height: auto !important; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; border-radius: 0px !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;">;</code></p>\r\n\r\n<div class="line number2 index1 alt1" style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); font-size: 13px; background-image: none !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; min-height: auto !important; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px 1em !important; border-radius: 0px !important;"><code class="js keyword" style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; background: none !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; font-weight: 700 !important; min-height: auto !important; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; border-radius: 0px !important; color: rgb(255, 120, 0) !important;">var</code>&nbsp;<code class="js plain" style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; background: none !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; min-height: auto !important; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; border-radius: 0px !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;">lastC&nbsp;=&nbsp;str.substring(str.length-1);</code></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="line number2 index1 alt1" style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); font-size: 13px; background-image: none !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; min-height: auto !important; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px 1em !important; border-radius: 0px !important;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="line number2 index1 alt1" style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); font-size: 13px; background-image: none !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; min-height: auto !important; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px 1em !important; border-radius: 0px !important;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, &quot;courier new&quot;, courier, 宋体, monospace; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;">截取最后一个字符串</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="line number2 index1 alt1" style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); font-size: 13px; background-image: none !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; min-height: auto !important; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px 1em !important; border-radius: 0px !important;">\r\n<pre accuse="aContent" class="best-text mb-10" id="best-content-1827716586" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, &quot;courier new&quot;, courier, 宋体, monospace; font-size: 16px; line-height: 29px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 55px;">\r\nvar str=&quot;abcd&quot;;\r\nvar newstr=str.substring(0,str.length-1);</pre>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>jq&nbsp;<code style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(0, 0, 221);">$(&quot;form&quot;).serialize()</code></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class="hljs-built_in" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap;">原生js原型方法：Object</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240);">.prototype.fun=function(){}</span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>http://developer.51cto.com/art/201505/475587.htm</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>原生js模拟jq选择器：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>function $(sel){ return document.qureySelectAll(sel);}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>//调用 $(&quot;#id&quot;) | $(&quot;.cls&quot;)[0] | $(&quot;div&quot;)<span style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);">[0]</span> | $(&quot;ul li:last-child&quot;)</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>DOM操作：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[代替jq的append]:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">- document.body.<span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">innerHTML+=</span>&quot;&lt;p&gt;xxx&lt;/p&gt;&quot;;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-&nbsp;<span style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);">document.body.insertAdjacentHTML(&#39;beforeend&#39;,&#39;&lt;p&gt;xxxx&lt;/p&gt;&#39;);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background: url(&quot;http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif&quot;) -498px -70px repeat-y scroll transparent; padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important;line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;&nbsp;var&nbsp;myDiv&nbsp;=&nbsp;document.createElement(<span class="string" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: blue; background-color: inherit;">&quot;div&quot;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; background-color: inherit;">);&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="alt" style="list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background: url(&quot;http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif&quot;) -498px -70px repeat-y scroll transparent; color: inherit; padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important;line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;&nbsp;myDiv.innerHTML&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class="string" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: blue; background-color: inherit;">&quot;xxx&quot;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; background-color: inherit;">;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="alt" style="list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background: url(&quot;http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif&quot;) -498px -70px repeat-y scroll transparent; color: inherit; padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important;line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; background-color: inherit;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);">document.body.insertBefore(myDiv,document.getElementById(&#39;a&#39;));</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="alt" style="list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background: url(&quot;http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif&quot;) -498px -70px repeat-y scroll transparent; color: inherit; padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important;line-height:16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background: url(&quot;http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif&quot;) -498px -70px repeat-y scroll transparent; padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important;line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;var&nbsp;frag&nbsp;=&nbsp;document.createDocumentFragment();&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background: url(&quot;http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif&quot;) -498px -70px repeat-y scroll transparent; padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important;line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; background-color: inherit;">&nbsp;&nbsp;var&nbsp;myDiv&nbsp;=&nbsp;document.createElement(<span class="string" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; c