0;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>CSS操作：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">var el=<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);">document.querySelector(</span><span class="string" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: blue; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre;">&quot;.xxx&quot;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre;">);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre;">//以下方法ie9及以下版本不支持</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">el<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre;">.classList.add(&quot;on&quot;);&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">el<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre;">.classList.remove(&quot;on&quot;);&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre;">if(</span>el<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre;">.classList.contains(&quot;on&quot;)){}</span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>事件绑定：<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);">//以下方法ie8及以下版本不支持</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">el.addEventListener(&quot;click&quot;,funName);</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">el.removeEventListener(&quot;click&quot;,funName);</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>-三元判断符：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>var a = a!==0 ? a : 0;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>二维三元：options.x ? 1 : 0 === options.x ? null : state.x</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- &amp;&amp; || :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>var a = arr &amp;&amp; arr[0]; //如arr不存在也不会报错</p>\r\n\r\n<p>var a = window.a || {}; //没有window.a就取值{}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>JSON.stringify()方法对对象参数序列化，在低版本IE中引用json2.js可以实现类似效果</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div>/*获取Url参数值*/</div>\r\n\r\n<div>function getQueryString(key){</div>\r\n\r\n<div>var reg = new RegExp(&quot;(^|&amp;)&quot;+key+&quot;=([^&amp;]*)(&amp;|$)&quot;);</div>\r\n\r\n<div>var result = window.location.search.substr(1).match(reg);</div>\r\n\r\n<div>return result?decodeURIComponent(result[2]):null;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>}</div>\r\n', '', '2016-12-11 15:13:49', '2019-02-13 18:10:11', 60),
(208, '', 0, '请求头部', NULL, '', '<p>请求头响应头中常用字段详解：<a href="http://www.jianshu.com/p/6e86903d74f7" target="_blank">http://www.jianshu.com/p/6e86903d74f7</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>xmlHttpRequest请求链接中有ip（即便是本地同ip地址）都会报跨域：后端文件加如下头部：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>header(&quot;Access-Control-Allow-Origin:*&quot;);</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>- xhr.setRequestHeader(&quot;Content-type&quot;, &quot;application/x-www-form-urlencoded;&quot;);<br />\r\n- xhr.setRequestHeader(&quot;token&quot;, &#39;xxx&#39;);</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;xhr.getResponseHeader(&quot;content-type&quot;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>xhr.setRequestHeader(&quot;Content-Type&quot;, &nbsp;&quot;contentType&quot;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>var xhr = window.ActiveXObject ? new ActiveXObject(&quot;Microsoft.XMLHTTP&quot;) : new XMLHttpRequest();</p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-19 09:04:49', '2019-03-01 04:42:07', 68),
(209, '', 0, 'token', NULL, '', '<p>Token一般用在两个地方:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1)防止表单重复提交、</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2)anti csrf攻击（跨站点请求伪造）​</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;">理解：app内嵌页面每次请求需要token验证，防止app以外的浏览器也能访问？</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">请求中发送token而不再是发送cookie能够防止CSRF(跨站请求伪造)。即使在客户端使用cookie存储token，cookie也仅仅是一个存储机制而不是用于认证。不将信息存储在Session中，让我们少了对session操作。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;"><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">使用tokens时，可以提供可选的权限给第三方应用程序。当用户想让另一个应用程序访问它们的数据，我们可以通过建立自己的API，得出特殊权限的tokens</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;">http://blog.csdn.net/u010288264/article/details/52004169</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2016-12-20 02:08:19', '2016-12-19 19:37:48', NULL),
