(267, '', 0, 'Sublime Text 3 插件', NULL, '', '<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;"><a class="A ttl_ mark_undefined" style="color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" target="_blank">Sublime Text：</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--Sublime Text自带的代码格式化：<span style="color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 21.06px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Edit - Line - Reindent（编辑 - 行 - 再次缩进）</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">--自动换行：选择 &ldquo;Preferences&rdquo; 菜单，选择&nbsp;&ldquo;Settings - User&rdquo;，选择 &ldquo;Preferences&rdquo; 菜单，选择&nbsp;&ldquo;Settings - User&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>空格2改空格4：<br />\r\n- 全选<br />\r\n- 右下角选项点选&ldquo;转换为标签缩进&rdquo;<br />\r\n- 再点选&ldquo;标签宽度：4&rdquo;<br />\r\n- 再选回&ldquo;转换为空格缩进&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>支持vue：<a href="http://www.cnblogs.com/binlucky/p/6471351.html" target="_blank">http://www.cnblogs.com/binlucky/p/6471351.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.cnblogs.com/grimm/p/5767945.html" target="_blank">http://www.cnblogs.com/grimm/p/5767945.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>安装插件：-&nbsp;Ctrl+Shift+P &nbsp;-&gt; &nbsp;install Package -&gt; 要安装的插件</p>\r\n\r\n<p>删除插件：-&nbsp;Ctrl+Shift+P &nbsp;-&gt; &nbsp;remove&nbsp;Package -&gt; 要删除的插件</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>vue文件代码高亮：<a href="http://blog.csdn.net/ivy0_0/article/details/70311135" target="_blank">http://blog.csdn.net/ivy0_0/article/details/70311135</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-&nbsp;Ctrl+Shift+P &nbsp;-&gt; &nbsp;install Package &nbsp;-&gt; Vue Syntax Hightlight</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>sass：<a href="https://my.oschina.net/u/2487410/blog/749321" target="_blank">https://my.oschina.net/u/2487410/blog/749321</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>高亮 - Sass</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>自动格式化： Command + option + L &nbsp;// Control + alt + L</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>自动换行：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Preferences -&gt; Settings - User -&gt; 设置<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: verdana, &quot;ms song&quot;, 宋体, Arial, 微软雅黑, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&quot;word_wrap&quot;: true</span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>符号说明：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">⌘：command&nbsp;<br />\r\n⌃：control&nbsp;<br />\r\n⌥：option&nbsp;<br />\r\n⇧：shift&nbsp;<br />\r\n↩：enter&nbsp;<br />\r\n⌫：delete&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">安装 SublimeLinter &nbsp; /&nbsp;&nbsp;SublimeLinter-contrib-eslint</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;"><a href="http://www.jianshu.com/p/e826e13c67ec" target="_blank">http://www.jianshu.com/p/e826e13c67ec</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>格式化代码：选择代码，ctrl+alt+f</p>\r\n', '', '2017-05-14 10:00:37', '2019-03-02 05:56:26', 30),
(268, '', 0, 'Vue.js开发经验', NULL, '', '<p>-在应用启动时，可以通过设置 Vue.config.productionTip = false 关闭生产模式下给出的提示</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-对象赋值为不互相影响：(得到深拷贝的原始数据对象而不会共享引用)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">var b = JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(a));</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">或 var b = [].concat(a);</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--$event.target拿到最底层的Dom，$event.currentTarget拿到当前的Dom</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>有时有数组下标的值无法更新，使用set方法或splice方法：<a href="http://blog.csdn.net/lucky_lxg/article/details/67634293" target="_blank">http://blog.csdn.net/lucky_lxg/article/details/67634293</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">this.checks.splice(index, 1, !this.checks[index]);</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">data定义的对象或数组，其属性第一次设置可以渲染成功，而如果要更改或删除要以下方法才能重新渲染：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">--this.$set(obj,param,val); &nbsp;/ this.$set(arr,index,val);</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">--arr.splice(index,1,val);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><s>弹窗的显隐都放在子组件自行控制，包括transition过渡效果，closeWindow除关掉自己可执行父组件对应共享的关闭方法！！--2017-7-20</s></p>\r\n\r\n<p>子组件的显隐和过渡都放在父组件实现，closeWindow从子组件传递方法给父组件：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">父组件：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&lt;transition class=&quot;transWin&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;">&lt;child v-if=&quot;activeWin&quot; @touchmove=&quot;noScroll&quot; :close=&quot;closeWin&quot;&gt;&lt;/child&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&lt;/transition&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">js : closeWin () {...}</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">子组件：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">一般的html和css，关闭控件：&lt;a @click=&quot;closeWin&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">js：props:[&#39;close&#39;], &nbsp;closeWin () {this.close()}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.vue模版数据结构注意：如值为undefined时访问其属性会报错，防止数据未加载前发生此情况</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 遍历数据到三级以上的需注意</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>mounted () {</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">document.body.appendChild(this.$el)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 这样可以把当前的组件直接放到body的下一级，适用于弹窗mask能覆盖整屏</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>一个组件里同个数据的多个状态处理：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>（情景一：城市选择，有默认值，选择后hightlight，确定后显示到指定位置）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>（情景二：下拉选择后搜索，默认值，下拉选择后，及搜索提交后）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>三个状态：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">默认值：defVal,&nbsp; // 一开始就保存起来以便后面恢复，用JSON.parse(JSON.stringify())深拷贝原值</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">点选时：tempVal, // 也许跟curVal显示位置不同，或暂时显示以便返回时恢复curVal，所以要另起一个状态</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">确定后：trueVal //</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style="color:#B22222;">组件和组件传参时不要直接修改传参值，（有些组件会报错），可以通过修改对象下的属性值来传参</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>如果你要传递的不是单条数据，而是一个对象，可以使用同类深度监听<br />\r\nwatch:{<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;data&#39;:{<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; handler:function(newValue,oldValue){<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; doSomeThing();<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; },<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; deep:true<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; }<br />\r\n}</p>\r\n', '', '2017-05-21 02:37:14', '2019-09-25 08:22:21', 85),
(269, '', 0, 'vue-cli脚手架', NULL, '', '<p>官网：<a href="https://cli.vuejs.org/zh/" target="_blank">https://cli.vuejs.org/zh/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">vue-cli3.x</span>版本安装搭建：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">如已安装2.x，需要先卸载：$ npm uninstall vue-cli -g 或 yarn global remove vue-cli</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">$ cnpm install&nbsp;-g @vue/cli 或 yarn global add @vue/cli</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">$&nbsp;vue create test2&nbsp; // 快速创建,可选default默认配置；也可用vue init webpack test2来创建</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">$ cd test2</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">（cli3的webpack配置在:&nbsp;/node_modules 目录下 @vue 中的 cli-service）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">（$&nbsp;vue inspect &gt; output.js&nbsp;, 这样我们会得到一份最终生效的 webpack 配置信息，省得去看 cli-service 源码）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">自定义配置：根目录下自己新建一个vue.config.js，并在其中配置自定义选项</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">$ npm run serve</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>vue-cli2.x版本安装搭建：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">( $ npm install cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org -g )</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">$ cnpm install vue-cli -g</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">$ vue init webpack Vue-Project</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">$ cd Vue-Project</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">$ cnpm install&nbsp; // 可能上上步骤已经安装好了，可以跳过</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">$ npm run dev</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>vue-cli里的配置文件分析：<a href="http://blog.csdn.net/hongchh/article/details/55113751" target="_blank">http://blog.csdn.net/hongchh/article/details/55113751</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>vue-cli3的vue.config.js配置：<a href="https://cli.vuejs.org/zh/config/#devserver-proxy">https://cli.vuejs.org/zh/config</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>/static - 存放第三方静态资源；里面的.gitkeep保证文件为空时也能提交到git仓库</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.babeIrc - presets预设，设置预先需要安装的插件；comments:false转换后代码不生成注释</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.editorconfig - 编辑器的配置</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.eslintignore - 忽略语法检查的目录文件</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.eslintrc.js - eslint的配置文件 ; 可以对不需要的检测规则属性设置为0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;no-debugger&#39;: process.env.NODE_ENV===&#39;production&#39;?2:0; 生成环境不能debug</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;semi&#39;:[&#39;error&#39;,&#39;always&#39;] &nbsp;//可以加分号</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;indent&#39;:0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;/*eslint-disable no-new*/</p>\r\n\r\n<p>webStorm自动格式化：Command + option + L &nbsp; ( win：Control _ alt + L )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>devMiddleware - &nbsp;中间件，把编译好的代码放在内存里，让浏览器只对内存做访问</p>\r\n\r\n<p>让json数据格式化 - 安装Google的jsonview插件</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-手动在config.json中添加一个模块，执行名命令npm install 只安装新增的模块</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>模拟数据：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>根目录data.json:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">{&quot;goods&quot;:[</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">{&#39;&quot;name&quot;:&quot;aaa&quot;,&quot;price&quot;:&quot;$100&quot;},</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">{&#39;&quot;name&quot;:&quot;bbb&quot;,&quot;price&quot;:&quot;$200&quot;}</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">]}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>dev-server.js设置：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">var apiRoutes=express.Router();<br />\r\napiRoutes.get(&#39;/list&#39;,function(req,res){<br />\r\n&nbsp; res.json({<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; code:0,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; data:require(&#39;../client/assets/api/menu.json&#39;)<br />\r\n&nbsp; });<br />\r\n});<br />\r\napp.use(&#39;/api&#39;,apiRoutes);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 这样浏览器访问 localhost/api/list就能拿到data.json的数据了</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style="color:#FF0000;">Use arrow keys</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n- 解决1：有些老版本的gitbash和node配合有问题。换最新版gitbash和node就好<br />\r\n- 解决2：输入选项的序号，排在第一个序号为1，以此类推，再按Enter就可以了</p>\r\n', '', '2017-05-25 17:24:38', '2019-08-17 01:56:14', 118),
(270, '', 0, 'node创建服务器', NULL, '', '<p>-根目录创建server.js,代码如下：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">var http = require(&#39;http&#39;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">http.createServer(function (request, response) {</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;// 发送 HTTP 头部&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;// HTTP 状态值: 200 : OK<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;// 内容类型: text/plain<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;response.writeHead(200, {&#39;Content-Type&#39;: &#39;text/plain&#39;});</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;// 发送响应数据 &quot;Hello World&quot;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;response.end(&#39;Hello World &#39;);<br />\r\n}).listen(8888);</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">// 终端打印如下信息<br />\r\nconsole.log(&#39;Server running at http://127.0.0.1:8888/&#39;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- node server.js</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 浏览器访问http://127.0.0.1:8888</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>app.listen(3000) //tcp6<br />\r\napp.listen(3000, &#39;0.0.0.0&#39;) //tcp</p>\r\n', '', '2017-05-25 17:28:56', '2019-01-03 05:21:04', 21),
(271, '', 0, 'sass相关', NULL, '', '<p>官网：<a href="http://sass-lang.com/" target="_blank">http://sass-lang.com/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>中文文档：<a href="https://www.sass.hk/docs/" target="_blank">https://www.sass.hk/docs/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>vue-cli支持sass：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="color:#B22222;">npm install --save-dev sass-loader</span><br />\r\n//因为sass-loader依赖于node-sass，所以还要安装node-sass<br />\r\n<span style="color:#B22222;">npm install --save-dev node-sass</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">//&nbsp;以上操作使用sass在dev下已经可以运行了，有些版本需要再在webpack.base.conf.js添加：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;"> {</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; test: /.scss$/,</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; loaders: [&quot;style&quot;, &quot;css&quot;, &quot;sass&quot;]</span><br />\r\n<span style="background-color:#E6E6FA;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; },</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">------------------------------下面是打包配置-------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">//解析.scss文件,对于用 import 或 require 引入的sass文件进行加载，以及&lt;style lang=&quot;sass&quot;&gt;...&lt;/style&gt;声明的内部样式进行加载<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="color:#B22222;"> test: /.scss$/,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; loader: ExtractTextPlugin.extract(&quot;style&quot;, &#39;css!sass&#39;)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 34, 34);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>//这里用了样式分离出来的插件，如果不想分离出来，可以直接这样写 <span style="color:#B22222;">loader:&#39;style!css!sass&#39;</span><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">-------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">vue中写法如：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&lt;style lang=&quot;scss&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n$a : green;<br />\r\n.eHead{<br />\r\n&nbsp; color: $a;<br />\r\n}<br />\r\n&lt;/style&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>安装 node-sass 的正确姿势：<a href="https://github.com/lmk123/blog/issues/28" target="_blank">https://github.com/lmk123/blog/issues/28</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>有时候<span style="color:#FF0000;">node-sass</span>怎么都<span style="color:#FF0000;">安装不上</span>，貌似可以用下面的替换：</p>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&quot;sass&quot;:&nbsp;&quot;^1.18.0&quot;,</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&quot;sass-loader&quot;:&nbsp;&quot;^7.1.0&quot;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '2017-05-27 06:58:35', '2019-09-08 11:51:30', 86),
(272, '', 0, '浏览器', NULL, '', '<p>- chrome审查元素Sources查找文件名：Ctrl+o</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 谷歌的隐身窗口：作用在于可以不记录cookie和其它缓存文件以达到隐身的作用</p>\r\n\r\n<p>谷歌隐身模式，没有缓存</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>data数据格式化插件：Google的jsonview</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>chrome跨域设置：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>桌面新建/my文件夹，里面新建chrome快捷键，右击选&#39;属性&#39; -&gt; 快捷方式 :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>目标 在原有的后面加如下：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;--disable-web-security --user-data-dir=C:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/my</p>\r\n\r\n<p>确定后此chrome打开的链接就可以跨域了</p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>家里设置的是：&nbsp;--args --disable-web-security --user-data-dir</p>\r\n\r\n<p>没有新建my文件，直接桌面上的chrome第一个页面就可以跨域</p>\r\n', '', '2017-05-29 07:48:37', '2019-07-25 12:40:29', 108),
(273, '', 0, 'form控件注意事项', NULL, '', '<p>&lt;label for=&quot;a&quot;&gt;A&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; id=&quot;a&quot; value=&quot;A&quot; /&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// label的for值对应checkbox的id，这样当点击label时checkbox会联动selected</p>\r\n\r\n<p>也可以写成下面格式有同样的效果：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;label for=&quot;a&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; id=&quot;a&quot; value=&quot;A&quot; /&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&lt;span&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;/label&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2018-01-08 14:34:20', '2018-01-08 02:34:28', NULL),
(274, '', 0, 'autoprefixer', NULL, '', '<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">自动补全css3前缀：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">var autoprefixer = require(&#39;autoprefixer&#39;);<br />\r\nmodule.exports={<br />\r\n&nbsp; //其他配置这里就不写了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp; module:{<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; loaders:[<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; test:/.css$/,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; //在原有基础上加上一个postcss的loader就可以了<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; loaders:[&#39;style-loader&#39;,&#39;css-loader&#39;,&#39;postcss-loader&#39;]<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ]<br />\r\n&nbsp; },<br />\r\n&nbsp; postcss:[autoprefixer({browsers:[&#39;last 2 versions&#39;]})]</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">}</p>\r\n', '', '2017-12-30 06:48:54', '2017-12-29 18:48:43', 92),
(275, '', 0, 'eslint相关', NULL, '', '<p>- 对 var 报错</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 挂载到window下的属性调用时前面也要加上window</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>eslint三标准：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------------<br />\r\n1 - eslint-config-google<br />\r\n2 - eslint-config-airbnb<br />\r\n3 - eslint-config-standard</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// vue-cli在安装的时候可以选择 3 或 2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>参考：</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/LO-ME/p/8080348.html" target="_blank">https://www.cnblogs.com/LO-ME/p/8080348.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/macliu/p/9489391.html" target="_blank">https://www.cnblogs.com/macliu/p/9489391.html</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/helpzp2008/article/details/51507428" target="_blank">https://blog.csdn.net/helpzp2008/article/details/51507428</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq940853667/article/details/77183961" target="_blank">https://blog.csdn.net/qq940853667/article/details/77183961</a>&nbsp; （详细说明，no-tabs等）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>英文官网API：</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://eslint.org/docs/rules/" target="_blank">https://eslint.org/docs/rules/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2017-06-13 08:46:01', '2019-01-26 13:07:52', 87),
(276, '', 0, '数据请求经验', NULL, '', '<p>-请求是json文件确保每个{}对象最后的属性不要带&#39;,&#39;逗号，否则获取的是字符串，而非对象？</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-请求的json文件要{}对象或[]数组包裹</p>\r\n', '', '2017-06-13 09:45:57', '2018-12-27 07:07:58', 64),
(277, '', 0, '注意事项', NULL, '', '<p>vue入口index.html添加静态css和js：<br />\r\n<a href="https://segmentfault.com/q/1010000004479605/a-1020000004486366" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: block; max-width: 400px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;" target="_blank">https://segmentfault.com/q/1010000004479605/a-1020000004486366</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="hljs php" style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;"><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; padding: 0px; color: inherit; background: none; border-radius: 0px; white-space: initial; overflow-wrap: normal; word-break: break-word;">app.<span class="hljs-keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">use</span>(<span class="hljs-string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);">&#39;/assets&#39;</span>,express.<span class="hljs-keyword" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">static</span>(<span class="hljs-string" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);">&#39;./src/assets&#39;</span>));</code></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="hljs php" style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:18px;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><strong><span style="color:#B22222;">productionTip</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:18px;"><span style="font-size:14px;">2.2.0 新增</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:18px;"><span style="font-size:14px;">设置为 false 以阻止 vue 在启动时生产模式下生成提示</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:18px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">如在main.js中设置 :&nbsp;</span>Vue.config.productionTip = false</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:18px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2017-06-14 01:18:00', '2019-01-18 12:43:16', 78),
(278, '', 0, '——待处理问题', NULL, '', '<div>&lt;ul&gt;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="margin-left: 40px;">&lt;li v-for = &quot;(val,key) in obj&quot; :data-key=&quot;key&quot; v-text=&quot;val&quot;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&lt;/ul&gt;</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Vue.use(Plugins) - 调用其install方法添加Vue的全局属性/方法/资源/实例方法等</p>\r\n\r\n<p>new Plygins时实例挂载到Vue里还是window?</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>移动端 html font-size ：</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.jianshu.com/p/afbf518cc891" target="_blank">http://www.jianshu.com/p/afbf518cc891</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://codepen.io/romanrudenko/pen/GrqcI" target="_blank">&nbsp;https://codepen.io/romanrudenko/pen/GrqcI</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>-vue 动画</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre;">animation-duration ？</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-new Router</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">mode: &#39;hash&#39;,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;VueAuth</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;animate.css</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;sync(store, router)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>import axios from &#39;axios&#39;<br />\r\nimport VueAxios from &#39;vue-axios&#39;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vue.use(VueAxios, axios)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>axios.defaults.baseURL = &#39;http://api.eg.com/index.php&#39;,<br />\r\naxios.defaults.timeout = 10000;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(234, 248, 230);">&lt;template&gt;img src用相对路径可以，如果用别名该怎么添加？？测试好像使用vue-cli默认的@别名无效</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>-proxyTable：代理接口，哪些接口要转发</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-resolveLoader？</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>-组件的template属性值html换行要加&#39;&#39;，否则报错？</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>用jq操作DOM后后面的vue渲染有时候会有问题，如jq修改的text后面vue切换没有正确渲染</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>extend 是 vue 用预定义选项来创建可复用组件的构造器&nbsp;&nbsp;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>服务器渲染：<a href="https://www.imooc.com/article/28337" target="_blank">https://www.imooc.com/article/28337</a></p>\r\n', '', '2017-07-02 08:54:02', '2019-03-21 12:38:55', 85),
(279, '', 0, '实体', NULL, '', '<div>空格<span style="white-space: pre;"> -- </span>&amp;nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&lt;<span style="white-space: pre;"> -- </span>小于号<span style="white-space: pre;"> -- </span>&amp;lt;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&gt;<span style="white-space: pre;"> -- </span>大于号<span style="white-space: pre;"> -- </span>&amp;gt;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&amp;<span style="white-space: pre;"> -- </span>和号<span style="white-space: pre;"> -- </span>&amp;amp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&quot;<span style="white-space: pre;"> -- </span>引号<span style="white-space: pre;"> -- </span>&amp;quot;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>更多参考：</div>\r\n\r\n<div><a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/html/html_entities.asp" target="_blank">http://www.w3school.com.cn/html/html_entities.asp</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div><a href="http://tool.xker.com/htmlchar.php" target="_blank">http://tool.xker.com/htmlchar.php</a></div>\r\n', '', '2017-07-05 02:56:42', '2018-12-26 18:09:44', 52),
(280, '', 0, '报错', NULL, '', '<p>SyntaxError: Unexpected token o in JSON at position 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----可能是对一个不是字符串（对象）执行了JSON.parse</p>\r\n', '', '2017-07-18 08:43:23', '2017-07-17 20:54:57', NULL),
(281, '', 0, 'swiper', NULL, '', '<p>使用注意:<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;---有自动添加各种类名证明实例成功了<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;---其他一起滚动的内容跟swiper-slider同级<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;---下拉加载占用物理空间，跟swiper-slider同级，且也加上类名swiper-slider<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;---上拉加载用margin-top让加载图标停留一段时间<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;---上拉刷新图标absolute + 0<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;-------swiper-container -&gt; 可视滚动高度 （需要固定高度）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">js设置其高度：obj.style.height = (document.documentElement.clientHeight - swiper容器外区域的高度) + &#39;px&#39;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;-------swiper-wrapper -&gt; 100%<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;-------swiper-slider -&gt; li的外容器，实际高度</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>获取translate：Swiper.translate;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>设置translate： Swiper.setWrapperTranslate(0);</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>在vue组件中使用swiper最后不要在mounted实例，而watch回调中数据加载完且this.$nextTick后实例</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>最大滚动距离：self.swiper.slides[0].offsetHeight</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>- swiper插件使用:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">new swiper($(&#39;#div&#39;),function(){ 参数 });</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&lt;div #div&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&lt;div class=&quot;swiper-wrapper&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;">&lt;div class=&quot;swiper-slide&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;">&lt;div class=&quot;swiper-slide&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n', '', '2017-07-20 01:12:35', '2017-12-30 02:30:02', 94),
(282, '', 0, '入门', NULL, '', '<p>文档：<a href="https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/api/" target="_blank">https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/api/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>rpx 根据屏幕宽度进行自适应。规定屏幕宽为750rpx<br />\r\n如在 iPhone6 上，屏幕宽度为375px，共有750个物理像素，则750rpx = 375px = 750物理像素，1rpx = 1px？</p>\r\n', '', '2019-01-04 08:20:44', '2019-03-05 17:22:32', 99);
INSERT INTO `point` (`id`, `pid`, `sort`, `title`, `attr`, `description`, `extend`, `subFieldSet`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`, `lineId`) VALUES
(283, '', 0, '## transition过渡效果', NULL, '', '<p>&lt;transition name=&quot;test&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&lt;div class=&quot;aaa&quot; v-if=&quot;openState&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">...</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&lt;/div&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;/transition&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.test-enter-active, .test-leave-active {</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">transition: transform 0.5s ease;<br />\r\ntransform: scale(1);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.test-enter, .test-leave-active {</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">transition: transform 0s ease;<br />\r\ntransform: scale(0);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>样式设置fixed + bottom:0;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>从下往上弹出：</p>\r\n\r\n<div>.test-enter-active, .test-leave-active {</div>\r\n\r\n<div>transition: bottom 0.4s;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>bottom: 0!important;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>}</div>\r\n\r\n<div>.test-enter, .test-leave-active {</div>\r\n\r\n<div>transition: bottom 0s;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>bottom: -100%!important;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>}</div>\r\n\r\n<p>// vue transition是针对v-if和v-show的过渡效果设置</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 有时候无效可能是原设置的样式覆盖了，可在过渡设置的样式后加!important;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 可设置过渡时间长些来在谷歌浏览器查看过渡类名下设置的值</p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>fade-enter：进入过渡的开始状态，元素被插入时生效，只应用一帧后立即删除；</p>\r\n\r\n<p>fade-enter-active：进入过渡的结束状态，元素被插入时就生效，在过渡过程完成之后移除；</p>\r\n\r\n<p>fade-leave：离开过渡的开始状态，元素被删除时触发，只应用一帧后立即删除；</p>\r\n\r\n<p>fade-leave-active：离开过渡的结束状态，元素被删除时生效，离开过渡完成之后被删除；</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>渐进渐显效果：</p>\r\n\r\n<div>.transShopHead-enter-active, .transShopHead-leave-active {</div>\r\n\r\n<div>transition: opacity&nbsp;.4s;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>opacity: 1;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>}</div>\r\n\r\n<div>.transShopHead-enter, .transShopHead-leave-active {</div>\r\n\r\n<div>transition: opacity&nbsp;.4s;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>opacity: 0;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>}</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&lt;transition<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; mode=&quot;out-in&quot;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; enter-active-class=&quot;fadeIn&quot;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; leave-active-class=&quot;fadeOut&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;appear</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;div class=&quot;bbb&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/transition&gt;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '2017-07-20 01:30:21', '2019-01-03 05:12:43', 85),
(284, '', 0, 'qmyg项目开发笔记', NULL, '', '<p>-弹窗子组件自行控制显隐和过渡效果</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-字段：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">状态:：activeWin</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">通过commit({type:&#39;activeWin&#39;, activeWin:true})来切换;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">打开方法：openWin</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">一般是父组件调用</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">关闭方法：closeWin</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">一般是子组件调用，除关闭自身外，判断是否有共享的closeWin方法来调用执行其他如关闭覆盖层等的操作</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>this.$store.get.commit({ type: &#39;openAddr&#39;, openAddr: true, stateKey: &#39;AddressSelect&#39;});</p>\r\n\r\n<p>//&nbsp;stateKey表明哪个组件的，如被多个调用时设置为空；本身组件的不用stateKey</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>--（npm run build）编译前先把/vhosts/nginx.conf的42行proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:1988/;注释</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--重启nginx : nginx -s reload</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>walle瓦力发布：提交上线单 -》 测试环境 -&gt; 标题、选最新版本develop 提交 -&gt; 上线</p>\r\n', '', '2017-07-20 14:07:39', '2017-08-18 02:24:52', 19),
(285, '', 0, '移动端经验', NULL, '', '<p>用swiper的translate滑动比原生的scroll的好处：来回滚动时fixed元素不会消失再显示（这问题还没找到解决的方法）</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>如果设置某容器width:105%（超过100%）,其外容器一定到overflow，否则移动端测试会把整屏撑开</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>整页面外容器不要设在body上，移动端貌似高度不明确，（background:bottom时出问题）如把外容器设置在body内的div内没有这个问题</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>jeDate插件不要用input控件来触发，手机端会弹出键盘，而jeDate的弹窗确不会弹出</p>\r\n', '', '2017-08-08 09:11:56', '2017-08-28 20:57:33', 19),
(286, '', 0, '图片加载失败用默认图片替换', NULL, '', '<p>vue:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&lt;img :src=&quot;item.thumb&quot; @error=&quot;errorImg(item)&quot; /&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">methords:{</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">errorImg (img) {</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px;">this.$set(item, &#39;thumb&#39;, &#39;http://www.eggou.com/images/errorImg.png&#39;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">}</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">}</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">--------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>&nbsp;for&nbsp;(let&nbsp;i&nbsp;=&nbsp;0;i&nbsp;&lt;&nbsp;document.images.length;&nbsp;i&nbsp;++)&nbsp;{<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(document.images[i].readyState&nbsp;!==&nbsp;&#39;complete&#39;)&nbsp;{<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;document.images[i].src&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;http://www.eggou.com/images/errorImg.png&#39;;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br />\r\n}</div>\r\n\r\n<div>// 测试有问题</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>setTimeout(function () {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; for (let i in self.$refs.img) {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; console.log(self.$refs.img[i]);<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; self.$refs.img[i].onerror = function () {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; console.log(this);<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; };<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; }, 3000);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 待测试</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '2017-07-22 09:37:21', '2017-07-21 21:57:38', 19),
(287, '', 0, '实例', NULL, '', '<p>按需加载（懒加载）：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>const A&nbsp; &nbsp; = resolve =&gt; require([&#39;./components/a&#39;], resolve);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>export const xxx = () =&gt; import(&#39;./index.vue&#39;); --- // webpack 语法</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>获取当前模块dom：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>this.$el</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>把当前模块放到body下一级：（有时候需要相对body做fixed定位）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>document.body.appendChild(this.$el)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>内置样式通过computed赋值：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;div :style=&quot;[xxxStyle]&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>computed: {</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">xxxStyle () {</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">return true ? {&#39;margin-left&#39;: 0} : null</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>监听多个对象（A,B,C）都变化了实例swiper一次，以后的update只监听C:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">data - a=0, b=0, swiperWatch = 0;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">computed - A = 列表数组A, B = 列表数组B, C = 列表数组C</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">watch :</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">A -&gt; a = 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">B -&gt; b = 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">C -&gt; if (a &amp;&amp; b) { this.swiperWatch = Math.random(); C = 列表数组}</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; else { C=Math.random()&nbsp;}</p>\r\n', '', '2017-07-25 03:32:52', '2019-08-10 07:46:40', 85),
(288, '', 0, '原理相关', NULL, '', '<p>v-if : false时数据已经加载，只是没有渲染</p>\r\n\r\n<p>v-show : false时渲染出来了，只是没有显示</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>组件v-if false是mounted获取不到$refs，因为dom还没有渲染</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>updated时dom已经更新渲染</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>computed执行时还没有mounted，但可以访问this</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#B22222;">&lt;keep-alive&gt;</span>是Vue的内置组件，能在组件切换过程中将状态保留在内存中，防止重复渲染DOM<br />\r\n和 &lt;transition&gt; 相似，&lt;keep-alive&gt; 是一个抽象组件：它自身不会渲染一个 DOM 元素，也不会出现在父组件链中。<br />\r\n<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/sysuhanyf/p/7454530.html" target="_blank">https://www.cnblogs.com/sysuhanyf/p/7454530.html</a></p>\r\n', '', '2017-07-27 21:56:18', '2019-04-08 07:48:29', 85),
(289, '', 0, '组件之间的数据传递', NULL, '', '<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">父 &nbsp;传数据-》 子</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">父 传方法-》 子</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">子 传数据-》 父</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">子 传方法-》 父</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">父 触发 子 方法</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">子 触发 父 方法</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>this.$refs.child.test();</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">子组件给父组件传参：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">子组件：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&lt;div @click=&quot;bbb&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">methods: {</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">bbb () { this.$emit(&#39;bbb&#39;, &#39;infoTxt&#39;); }</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">}</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">父组件：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&lt;child @bbb=&quot;aaa&quot;&gt;&lt;/child&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">methods: {</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">aaa (txt) {</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 120px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">alert(txt); //&nbsp;<span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">infoTxt</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">}</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">}</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">// $emit第二个参数主要用于传递数据，不用时主要是传递方法</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">-----------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">另一种方法：(例：子组件向父组件传swiper实例，方便update())</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">父组件：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&lt;child :get-swiper=&quot;getSwiper&quot;&gt;&lt;/child&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">methods: {</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">getSwiper (swiperObj) {...} // 传递方法同时也传递参数</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">}</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">子组件：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">prop: [&#39;getSwiper&#39;]</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">if (getSwiper) {</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 80px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">getSwiper(swiperObj);</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">}</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>通过vuex来传递数据：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>vuex配置：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">test: false,</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">action: 0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>a组件：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">this.$store.commit(&#39;test&#39;,true)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">。。。</p>\r\n', '', '2017-08-02 13:18:30', '2019-01-03 05:16:29', 85),
