(572, '', 0, 'iconfont的使用', NULL, '', '<p>iconfont下载代码里有三种生成<span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">矢量图标</span>的方式：fontclass/unicode/symbol</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 中台用的是symbol</p>\r\n\r\n<p>使用和比较：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/wu08518/article/details/79098464" target="_blank">https://blog.csdn.net/wu08518/article/details/79098464</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>svg矢量图标设置颜色用fill:red; ?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>font class的使用：<br />\r\n===============================<br />\r\nimport &#39;./iconfont.css&#39;;<br />\r\n---------<br />\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;iconfont icon-xxx&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Symbol的使用：<br />\r\n===============================<br />\r\nimport &#39;./iconfont.js&#39;;<br />\r\n---------<br />\r\n&lt;svg class=&quot;icon&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &lt;use xlink:href=&quot;#icon-xxx&quot;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/svg&gt;<br />\r\n---------<br />\r\n.icon {<br />\r\n&nbsp; width: 1em;<br />\r\n&nbsp; height: 1em;<br />\r\n&nbsp; vertical-align: -0.15em;<br />\r\n&nbsp; fill: currentColor;<br />\r\n&nbsp; overflow: hidden;<br />\r\n}</p>\r\n', '', '2019-08-05 08:24:15', '2019-08-05 08:28:03', 119),
(573, '', 0, 'fortawesome的使用', NULL, '', '<p>官网：<a href="http://www.fontawesome.com.cn/faicons/">http://www.fontawesome.com.cn/faicons/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 需要把整个文件加载进来</p>\r\n\r\n<p>------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>@font-face {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; font-family: &#39;FontAwesome&#39;;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;src: url(&#39;../fonts/fontawesome-webfont.eot?v=4.7.0&#39;);<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;src: url(&#39;../fonts/fontawesome-webfont.eot?#iefix&amp;v=4.7.0&#39;) format(&#39;embedded-opentype&#39;), url(&#39;../fonts/fontawesome-webfont.woff2?v=4.7.0&#39;) format(&#39;woff2&#39;), url(&#39;../fonts/fontawesome-webfont.woff?v=4.7.0&#39;) format(&#39;woff&#39;), url(&#39;../fonts/fontawesome-webfont.ttf?v=4.7.0&#39;) format(&#39;truetype&#39;), url(&#39;../fonts/fontawesome-webfont.svg?v=4.7.0#fontawesomeregular&#39;) format(&#39;svg&#39;);<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;font-weight: normal;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;font-style: normal;<br />\r\n------------<br />\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;icon&quot;&gt;&amp;#xf2b9&lt;/div&gt;<br />\r\n------------<br />\r\n.icon {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;font-family: FontAwesome;<br />\r\n}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>在Vue中使用Font Awesome：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/zyj362633491/article/details/86422353">https://blog.csdn.net/zyj362633491/article/details/86422353</a></p>\r\n', '', '2019-08-05 08:29:24', '2019-08-05 08:54:03', 119),
