(600, '', 0, 'TypeORM', NULL, '', '<p>中文文档：<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/1c4650e3718a">https://www.jianshu.com/p/1c4650e3718a</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://www.allknowboy.com/posts/3f556577/">https://www.allknowboy.com/posts/3f556577/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>官网：<a href="https://typeorm.io/#/">https://typeorm.io/#/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>参考：</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_36279445/article/details/88310648">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_36279445/article/details/88310648</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://ruiming.me/typeorm-worth-a-try/">https://ruiming.me/typeorm-worth-a-try/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>@Column注解：</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/cnwyt/article/details/85099841">https://blog.csdn.net/cnwyt/article/details/85099841</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>@CreateDateColumn 需要 mysql 5.6.41以上版本：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>// 查看mysql版本是 5.5 设置默认值 CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(6) 失败 ,&nbsp;升级 mysql 为 5.6.41 即可</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>安装 &amp; 启动：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>npm install typeorm -g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>typeorm init --name 项目名称 --database mysql</p>\r\n\r\n<p>cd 项目名称<br />\r\nnpm install</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>修改数据库配置文件ormconfig.json，对应数据库开启来</p>\r\n\r\n<p>npm start 启动</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>模糊搜索：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-----------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>let rs = this.repository</div>\r\n\r\n<div>.createQueryBuilder(&#39;bit&#39;)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>.where(&quot;bit.content <span style="color:#FF0000;">LIKE</span> :param&quot;)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>.setParameters({</div>\r\n\r\n<div>param: &#39;%&#39;+kw</div>\r\n\r\n<div>})</div>\r\n\r\n<div>.getMany();</div>\r\n\r\n<div>return rs;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>createQueryBuilder - relations - RelationQueryBuilder :</div>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/b14936d9a4c5">https://www.jianshu.com/p/b14936d9a4c5</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>关联字段存数据库时后面不用加Id, 会自动加；如手动加了当是非关联字段处理</p>\r\n\r\n<p>如 post { point: 1 } , 存入数据库时是 pointId为1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>加默认值：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>@Column({ default: &#39;&#39; })</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '2019-08-18 01:31:56', '2019-09-08 06:23:37', 123),
(601, '', 0, '注意', NULL, '', '<p><span style="color:#FF0000;">:first-child</span><br />\r\n1.保证前面没有兄弟节点,要么就用div包住<br />\r\n2.img:first-of-type{}也能达到first-child的效果,且前面可以有节点<br />\r\n3.img:nth-of-type(1){}也能达到first-child的效果,且前面可以有节点</p>\r\n', '', '2019-08-18 01:36:04', '2019-08-18 01:35:50', 54),
