(671, '', 0, '待处理-以前记录的文学资料', NULL, '', '<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">我曾七次鄙视自己的灵魂：</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 它本可进取却故作谦卑；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 它在空虚时用爱欲来填充；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 在困难和容易之间它选择容易；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 它犯了错，却借由别人也会犯错来宽慰自己；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 它自由软弱，却把它认为是生命的坚韧；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 它鄙夷一张丑恶的嘴脸，却不知那正是自己面具中的一副；</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 它侧身于生活的污泥，虽不甘心却又畏首畏尾。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &mdash;&mdash;纪伯伦</p>\r\n\r\n<hr style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;" />\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">一切都是可以靠借的，可以借资金、借人才、借技术、借智慧。这个世界已经准备好了一切你所需要的资源，你所要做的仅仅是把他们收集起来，运用智慧把他们有机的组合起来</p>\r\n\r\n<hr style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;" />\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">四两拨千斤</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">早起的鸟儿有虫吃，早起的虫子被鸟吃。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">世界上最遥远的距离是我和你在一起，而你却在玩手机</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">丑到无可挑剔。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">如果丑是一种罪，你可以去判死刑了。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">其实!我是个二维码!很有内含!</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">你年轻么？不要紧，过两年就老了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">治的了你脾气的是你爱的人，受的了你脾气的是爱你的人。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">不公平就在于 男生有故事叫沧桑 女生有过去叫肮脏。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">重要的事情说三遍</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">人丑就要多读书</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">能靠长相吃饭 却偏偏要靠才华</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">吓死宝宝了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">这样真的好吗</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">带我装逼带我飞</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">也是醉了!</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">只想安静地做个美男子</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">不是告诉你下雨天要打伞的嘛 看吧 脑袋又进水了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">&ldquo;爱一个人就要大声说出来。&rdquo; &ldquo;出来!&rdquo;。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">我今天问电风扇我丑吗，它摇了一下午头！</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">不要对我有恨意，不要对我有爱意，更不要打我的主意，我正单身，当心我会在意。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">酒未醒，人醉了；酒醒后，酒瓶和心都碎了。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">说了你又不听，听又不懂，懂又不做，做又做错，错又不认，认又不改，改又不服，不服也不说，那叫我怎么办？</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">城会玩</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">然并卵</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">看脸的时代</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">刷脸</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">臣妾做不到</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">说走就走的旅行</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">闭目养神，闭嘴养心。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">快开学了，我的心已碎成二维码了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">当你成功了，说句屁话，也是真理。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">这天热的我都想吐舌头！</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">你是想死我了还是想我死了！</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">我在试衣间等你！</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">我是个可以靠脸吃饭的人，可我偏偏选择了不要脸！</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">你若安好，那还得了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">我可以亲你吗？不要脸！那好，亲嘴。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">大师兄，听说二师兄的肉，比师傅的都贵了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">跟爷谈感情，爷会让你死得很有层次感</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">如果你有鸭梨（压力），就把它放进冰箱里，让它变成冻梨（动力）。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">画面太美我不敢看</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">我很美，但是我美的特别，所以我特别的美！</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">不要迷恋哥，哥只会胡说！</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">谁傻谁知道</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">你丑你先走</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">世界那么大，我想去看看，你带上钱，我带着你，</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">工资就像大姨妈，一个月一次 ，一周左右就没了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">嗨，说多都是累啊！</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">我觉得你真的不是个合格的朋友，你还是改行做我老婆吧！</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">隐身，不是为了躲避谁，只是希望有谁发现我消失了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">A:为什么你又失眠？B:我在思考怎么不失眠。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">为兄弟两肋插刀,为情人插兄弟一刀.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">有一种痛苦，叫看着你们幸福。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">生活将我们磨圆，是为了让我们滚得更远</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">遇到你之前，我的世界是黑白的，遇见你之后，哇靠，全黑了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">有话好好说，别没事就坠楼</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">讨厌我的人多了，你算老几。</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">*************************************************************************</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">怪我咯</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">We are伐木累</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">我的内心几乎是崩溃的</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">上交给国家</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">秒懂</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">洗脑</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">人丑就要多读书</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">我也是醉了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">有钱就是任性</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">挖掘机技术哪家强</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">保证不打死你</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">我读书少你别骗我</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">且行且珍惜</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">no zuo no die（不作死就不会死）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">那么问题来了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">你家里人知道吗？</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">好有爱</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">脑残粉</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">什么仇什么怨</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">一百块都不给我</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">心塞</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">吓尿了</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">补刀</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">怎么破</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">你行你上</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">手滑</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, Tahoma, sans-serif;">要是你问蜈蚣，每次开始走路之前，先迈哪条腿，他也会疯掉的。</p>\r\n', '', '2017-12-17 13:05:00', '2018-10-29 01:38:32', 176),
(672, '', 0, '山河', NULL, '', '<p>五岳：东岳泰山，南岳衡山，西岳华山，北岳恒山，中岳嵩山</p>\r\n\r\n<p>衡山和恒山音同</p>\r\n\r\n<p>嵩song1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>---------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>祁连山 qi2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>秦岭-淮河 是南方和北方的分界线</p>\r\n\r\n<p>地形三级阶梯</p>\r\n\r\n<p>南岭</p>\r\n', '', '2018-02-10 10:31:15', '2018-02-20 18:00:24', 160),
(673, '', 0, '长隆', NULL, '', '<p><a href="https://sc.chimelong.com" target="_blank">https://sc.chimelong.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>长隆旗下拥有广州长隆与珠海长隆两大旅游度假区。旗下主题公园有欢乐世界、野生动物世界、水上乐园、国际大马戏、飞鸟乐园。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>广州长隆：欢乐世界、野生动物世界、水上乐园、飞鸟乐园</p>\r\n\r\n<p>珠海长隆：海洋王国、横琴国际马戏城</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '2018-02-11 07:09:59', '2018-02-10 19:10:46', 158),
(674, '', 0, '千灯湖-宜家', NULL, '', '<p>----------------------千灯湖-----</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>千灯湖位于广东省佛山市南海区桂城街道,至2017年，千灯湖已升级成为千灯湖中央公园，一共分四期:<br />\r\n老大（千灯湖一期）：2002年降生，占据了中心位置。球灯、水上茶亭等是它的特征，坐船可以饱览它的大部分美貌。<br />\r\n老二（原lei岗公园）：于2010年加入大家庭。老大与老二的分界线是海三路，往南是老二的地盘，包括文化广场、咏诗广场、金海桥、活水公园展示馆等。<br />\r\n老三（灯湖市政公园）：目前仍在&ldquo;扮靓靓&rdquo;，主要特征是建设灯湖广场。<br />\r\n老四（lei岗公园魁星阁）：它是个高个子，lei岗公园、魁星阁、千灯湖特色步行街等都记在它名下</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------宜家-----</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n-佛山宜家16年8月25日开业，营业面积超4万平方米，面积是广州的大三倍！目前华南地区最大的宜家商场<br />\r\n-公交可以搭G6路、桂16路、桂32路、沥15路、桂03路、南海快8路、173路等到千灯湖地铁站<br />\r\n-地铁：广佛线千灯湖站B出口<br />\r\n-自驾路线：佛山市中心&rarr;佛平路&rarr;佛平二路&rarr;桂澜中路（这条路不是高峰期基本不塞车。）<br />\r\n-停车：超过1500个室外停车位，抢室内停车场，地下2层，近500个停车位！<br />\r\n-自行车停车场，目测可以停100辆单车<br />\r\n-广佛同城，在广州宜家买的东西，可以在佛山宜家退货、提货等</p>\r\n', '', '2018-02-11 07:23:04', '2018-02-10 19:36:33', 159),
(675, '', 0, '祖庙', NULL, '', '<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-祖庙已经近千年历史，北宋元丰年间（1078&mdash;1085年）始建，现为国家级重点文物保护单位</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-佛山祖庙与肇庆悦城龙母庙、广州陈家祠合称为岭南古建筑三大瑰宝</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-来祖庙是拜北帝的(全称：</span>北方真武玄天上帝<span style="font-size:12px;">)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="line-height:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;">-佛山祖庙与肇庆悦城龙母庙、广州陈家祠合称为岭南古建筑三大瑰宝<br />\r\n-当时地区多为水乡,水患多,而北帝恰是传说中治水的神,于是北帝作为人的保护神被供奉起来<br />\r\n-里面出拜神外，还有粤剧看，还有免费的精彩舞狮，还有手工艺品卖，有各式狮头的纯手工制品，(听说外国人必买哦)，还有纯手工的石湾陶瓷公仔</span></p>\r\n', '', '2018-02-11 08:29:19', '2018-02-10 20:49:25', 159),
(676, '', 0, '同事', NULL, '', '<p>大学：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>赖俊钦，*彩香，熊慧敏，林卓沛，朱丹</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>09年：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>曾总，阿初</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10年：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>贝斯特：肖正平，郭裴，张晓慧(慧姐)，樊小秋，朱友明，张丽娜，刘曾丽，阿莲</p>\r\n\r\n<p>王昊</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>钻汇易：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>王迦南，黄晓</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>微壹购：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">吴春燕</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">黄泽耿&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;李伟豪&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;林伟健(Vison)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;张雪锋&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;陈聪&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 杨晓花&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 书藤</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>力德集团：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>丘爱鑫&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;徐雄彬&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 连锐鹏&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 刘吴强</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>广付科技</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>麦广扬&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;李华东&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;刘冉</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>小享科技：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">詹建军：潮汕&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;廖伟：四川内江市&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;白冰：河南秦皇岛？ （北戴河，杨肠子）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">曾江：梅州&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; penny(张佩霓)：湖南株洲&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;肇庆：陈广源，黄鹏，谭宝仪，黄佩珊</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">陈栋新：云浮罗定&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 黄锦彪：顺德（祖籍：英德）&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 石薇(4-13)：辽宁沈阳（夫：新疆）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">郭魏：辽宁沈阳&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;江西：李明，赖志勇（赣州）&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;广西：李柱华，姚运龙（普宁？）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">湖南：谭长清（株洲），彭明慧（郴州），陈栋（长沙），陈习</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">黄胜伟：广州？潮汕？湛江（深圳）</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">宋宁：河南&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 何玉龙&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;黄莉诗，慕容艳&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 志华&nbsp; 李柱华&nbsp; 谢宇恒&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;陈仁换</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">杨晶&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;树能&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;康敏武&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;KoKo&nbsp; 子嫦&nbsp; 文英&nbsp; 熊凯斌？</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">刘总&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;胡总&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;杨？</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>佳都（PCI）：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n\r\n<p>杨光(湖南怀化)&nbsp;--- 黄俊杰(惠州) --- 黄特金(湛江？茂名？)&nbsp;--- 陆婉冰(潮汕) --- 陈春桂(湛江？茂名？)</p>\r\n', '', '2018-02-12 02:53:27', '2019-08-24 02:08:00', 201),
(677, '', 0, '广州名山', NULL, '', '<p accuse="aContent" class="best-text mb-10" id="best-content-993422660" style="line-height:16px;">白云山（羊城八景之一）</p>\r\n\r\n<p accuse="aContent" class="best-text mb-10" style="line-height:16px;">越秀山（越秀公园内，有五羊雕像，镇海楼等）是白云山的余脉<br />\r\n大夫山（专骑自行车的）森林公园<br />\r\n莲花山（拜观音的）<br />\r\n帽峰山（吃烧鸡）森林公园，<span style="font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, 宋体, sans-serif, tahoma; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">老八区的最高峰（海拔534.9米）</span><br />\r\n火炉山（BBQ）森林公园</p>\r\n\r\n<p accuse="aContent">龙头山：位于黄埔区，森林公园<br />\r\n风云岭：位于从化市，登山健身好去处<br />\r\n大尖锋、小尖锋：位于从化市，三百洞生态度假区、广州境内最高山峰（海拔603米）</p>\r\n', '', '2018-02-12 06:43:45', '2018-02-11 18:52:57', 158),
